  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving Coffee and Haricot Beans export marketing activity</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p style=&apos;margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;text-align:justify;&apos;&gt;The 2020-year action plan will focus mainly on enhancing the union&amp;rsquo;s organizational development and improving the union coffee and haricot beans export marketing activity  specifically:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-size:11.0pt;&apos;&gt;Marketing and branding the union coffee to the internal buyers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-size:11.0pt;&apos;&gt;Crating better enabling marketing environment between the PCs and the union&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-size:11.0pt;&apos;&gt;Hiring 5 PC managers/accounts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-size:11.0pt;&apos;&gt;Raising the awareness of the union board and stakeholders about the importance of a professional HR in the union&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-size:11.0pt;&apos;&gt;Conducting value carter mission on coffee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;font-size:11.0pt;&apos;&gt;Improving the union governance &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p style=&apos;margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;text-align:justify;&apos;&gt;BHAG: &amp;nbsp;To become one of the best coffee and haircoat beans exporter&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&apos;margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;text-align:justify;&apos;&gt;Damota Wolayta Farmers&amp;rsquo; Cooperative Union Ltd (Damota) was found in 2003 as a secondary union cooperative with initially 26 primary member cooperatives (PC) and a capital of 295 000 Birr. Currently 68 primary cooperatives (with 24 594 farmers) are member. The capital of the union reached 21 655 390 Birr. The union has 32 permeant staffs. The union has an abundant potential for the production of different crops; like coffee  haricot beans  maize etc and fruits like mango  papaya and banana papaya. Currently  the union is export coffee in small quality (average 130 ton per year).&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot; sans-serif;&apos;&gt;Damota Wilayat union has been showing good track record in the past 3 years. In the future  it has a lot of business ambitions. But the union lacks clear prioritization of business ambitions and value chain developments. &amp;nbsp;In addition  on union level access to long term finance and working capital is of very large interest. Finance requests are not set up very systematically. furthermore  the union marketing activity  especially exportable goods could be improved and expanded. To fill this gap Agriterra providing a holistic capacity support to the union on the following areas: expanding of coffee marketing activities and the way red haricot beans sold  strengthening the union and its PCs relationship  professionalizing the management practice of the union and its affiliated &amp;nbsp;selected PCs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
